---
import Container from "../shared/Container.astro";
import Paragraph from "../shared/Paragraph.astro";
import Title from "../shared/Title.astro";

---

<section id="features">
    <Container className="flex ">
        <div class="p-5 text-center">
            <Title>
                We are here to code your frustrations away.
            </Title>
            <Paragraph className="mt-8">
                At Push Enhance, we understand the challenges and complexities that businesses face daily. That's why our dedicated team of experts is here to take the burden off your shoulders. With our passion for coding and problem-solving, we thrive on turning your frustrations into streamlined, efficient solutions. Whether it's customizing a EDI application, developing a new platform, or optimizing your workflows, we have the expertise to make it happen. Let us handle the technical aspects, so you can focus on what matters most - growing your business and achieving your dreams. Together, we'll code a brighter future for your enterprise.
            </Paragraph>
            <ul class="mt-8 space-y-4 text-heading-3 font-medium">
                <li>
                    <span class="font-bold bg-box-bg rounded-full w-8 h-8 mr-3 text-primary inline-flex justify-center items-center">&checkmark;</span> End to End EDI Planning and Development
                </li>
                <li>
                    <span class="font-bold bg-box-bg rounded-full w-8 h-8 mr-3 text-primary inline-flex justify-center items-center">&checkmark;</span> Consulting on exisiting project.
                </li>
                <li>
                    <span class="font-bold bg-box-bg rounded-full w-8 h-8 mr-3 text-primary inline-flex justify-center items-center">&checkmark;</span> Planning and Estimates.
                </li>
                <li>
                    <span class="font-bold bg-box-bg rounded-full w-8 h-8 mr-3 text-primary inline-flex justify-center items-center">&checkmark;</span> Outsource Development.
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="max-w-md mx-auto midmd:max-w-none lg:mx-0  lg:pr-10 xl:pr-2 flex-1 flex w-11/12 midmd:w-5/12 lg:w-1/2 midmd:h-auto">
            <div class="w-full h-80 sm:h-96 midmd:h-full relative">
                <div class="absolute rotate-45 -left-5 md:-left-10 lg:-left-20 xl:-left-24 p-1 top-1/2 w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-orange-400 blur-3xl opacity-50"></div>
                <div class="absolute  p-1 -top-4 md:-top-10 right-0 w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-orange-400 rounded-full blur-3xl opacity-60"></div>
                <span class="absolute w-full aspect-[16/5] -skew-x-12 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-tr from-primary to-green-400 opacity-40 blur-2xl left-0 bottom-0"></span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </Container>
</section>